ar.com.hjg.pngj.IBytesConsumer

  • Packages that use IBytesConsumer 
    Package Description
    ar.com.hjg.pngj
    PNGJ main package

    • Uses of IBytesConsumer in ar.com.hjg.pngj

      Classes in ar.com.hjg.pngj that implement IBytesConsumer 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  ChunkReader
      Parses a PNG chunk, consuming bytes in one of three modes: ChunkReader.ChunkReaderMode.BUFFER, ChunkReader.ChunkReaderMode.PROCESS, ChunkReader.ChunkReaderMode.SKIP.
      class  ChunkSeqBuffering
      This loads the png as a plain sequence of chunks, buffering all Useful to do things like insert or delete a ancilllary chunk.
      class  ChunkSeqReader
      Consumes a stream of bytes that consist of a series of PNG-like chunks.
      class  ChunkSeqReaderPng
      Adds to ChunkSeqReader the storing of PngChunk, with a PngFactory, and imageInfo + deinterlacer.
      class  ChunkSeqSkipping
      This simple reader skips all chunks contents and stores the chunkRaw in a list.
      class  DeflatedChunkReader
      Specialization of ChunkReader, for IDAT-like chunks.
      Methods in ar.com.hjg.pngj with parameters of type IBytesConsumer 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      int BufferedStreamFeeder.feed(IBytesConsumer consumer) 
      int BufferedStreamFeeder.feed(IBytesConsumer consumer, int maxbytes)
      Tries to feed the consumer with bytes read from the stream, at most maxbytes
      long BufferedStreamFeeder.feedAll(IBytesConsumer consumer)
      Feeds as much bytes as it can to the consumer, in a loop.
      int BufferedStreamFeeder.feedFixed(IBytesConsumer consumer, int nbytes)
      Feeds exactly nbytes, retrying if necessary
